gr.interamerican.bo2.jsqlparser.visitors
Class RemoveParameter

java.lang.Object
  gr.interamerican.bo2.jsqlparser.visitors.EmptyVisitor
      gr.interamerican.bo2.jsqlparser.visitors.RemoveParameter

public class RemoveParameter
extends EmptyVisitor

Rebuilds the an SQL statement by omitting the specified named parameter from its where clause(s). Queries with BETWEEN are not supported at the moment. Note that they can easily be written equivalently as two comparisons.
